divs: Sighting DetailsMe and my mother were outside looking at all of the airplanes then a huge UFO hovers over our house that's in shape of a boomerang but was not showing any light but left a path.only got a 10 second glare of it and then it disappeared in to the sky then when my sister was on her way home her car lost fuel in front of her friends house and they turned around and saw it and went straight inside her house.
Summary: UFO flew over top of house, silent,make car break down
